com.automatic.net

Class AutomaticClientPublic

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.automatic.net.AutomaticClientPublic

  • public class AutomaticClientPublic
extends java.lang.Object
    Internal SDK Class for making OAuth calls. Must be passed a clientId (OAuth client_id) and an oAuthHandler. Created by duncancarroll on 4/15/15.
